# Personal overrides for this repo

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` (which is gitignored) and edit it with your own per-repo
preferences. Anything here overrides the shared instructions in `AGENTS.md` (and `CLAUDE.md`).
Your global `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` still takes precedence over this file.

Delete the examples below and add your own.

